      <h3><img src="<%= asset_path('barbarajoycecraig.jpg') %>" width="400" height="271"><br>Barbara Joyce Craig </h3>
      <p><em>Hampton, GA<br>
          October, 2009 </em></p>
      <p>I haven't felt this good in more than ten years. My initial pain level with medication was eight out of ten. Now, after IDD Therapy&reg; treatment on the Accu-SPINA&reg; device, I'm 100% pain-free. I walked into the [clinic] with a cane; now I'm walking out without one. I used to be unable to drive; now I can drive. I used to need help getting out of the chair or tub; now I can do both by myself. I can now perform all the simple tasks I used to need pain medication to perform-but now I don't need the medication! I feel so good, I can just about do the Charleston dance! No back pain means I am not mad all the time. &nbsp; When I was hurting, nobody better get in my way and now I can't keep from talking to people and everyone likes me. You would be foolish not to get on IDD Therapy&reg;. </p>
